After successful login, users are required to specify the Source Folder Path by pasting it into the designated input field, as illustrated in the screenshot below.

The selected folder should contain all source files intended for processing in the current session. Each source file is expected to correspond to a single master rate record.

Note: The application currently supports only Excel files (.xlsx) as valid input sources.

Please refer to the following screenshots for an example of the user interface and the expected folder structure.

